For Windows: MPEG1 (VCD) most players; MPEG2 (DVD) freeware VLC, shareware player from http://www.elecard.com, or for-pay quicktime6 plugin: http://www.apple.com/quicktime/products/mpeg2playback/ ; MPEG4 quicktime6 from www.apple.com or VLC . Latest flash plugin for browsers.
